{
  "_meta": {
    "title": "Debug 找茬·分职业题库",
    "desc": "按 MinigameFlavor.key 分池：dev/test=代码；其余=职业文本挑错。字段同前：lines/bugLine/hint/explain/difficulty。",
    "schema": "pools.{flavorKey}: Puzzle[]  兼容旧版顶层 puzzles=dev"
  },
  "puzzles": [
    {
      "id": "p_range",
      "difficulty": "easy",
      "act": 1,
      "title": "数组越界",
      "lang": "python",
      "lines": [
        "def print_scores(scores):",
        "    for i in range(0, 4):",
        "        print(scores[i])",
        "",
        "print_scores([85, 92, 78])"
      ],
      "bugLine": 1,
      "hint": "循环跑了几次?列表有几个元素?",
      "explain": "range(0,4) 访问索引 0~3,但列表只有 3 个元素,第 4 次越界。应改成 range(len(scores))。"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_assign",
      "difficulty": "easy",
      "act": 1,
      "title": "该比较却赋值",
      "lang": "c",
      "lines": [
        "int check(int x) {",
        "    if (x = 5) {",
        "        return 1;",
        "    }",
        "    return 0;",
        "}"
      ],
      "bugLine": 1,
      "hint": "= 和 == 有什么区别?",
      "explain": "if (x = 5) 是赋值,恒为真。比较相等要用 ==。这是最经典的 C 语言坑。"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_return",
      "difficulty": "easy",
      "act": 1,
      "title": "忘了 return",
      "lang": "js",
      "lines": [
        "function add(a, b) {",
        "    const sum = a + b;",
        "}",
        "",
        "const r = add(2, 3);",
        "console.log(r); // undefined"
      ],
      "bugLine": 1,
      "hint": "函数把结果给出去了吗?",
      "explain": "算了 sum 却没 return,函数返回 undefined。第 2 行应为 return a + b。"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_eqeq",
      "difficulty": "easy",
      "act": 1,
      "title": "松散相等",
      "lang": "js",
      "lines": [
        "function isReady(v) {",
        "    if (v == null) return false;",
        "    if (v == 0) return false;",
        "    return true;",
        "}",
        "// isReady('') 竟然返回 false"
      ],
      "bugLine": 2,
      "hint": "== 会做类型转换,'' 会变成什么?",
      "explain": "v == 0 时 '' 被转成 0 判真,导致空字符串被误判。应该用 === 严格比较。"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_slice",
      "difficulty": "easy",
      "act": 2,
      "title": "切片少一个",
      "lang": "python",
      "lines": [
        "def last_three(items):",
        "    return items[-3:-1]",
        "",
        "# 期望拿最后 3 个,却只拿到 2 个"
      ],
      "bugLine": 1,
      "hint": "-1 是取到哪里?",
      "explain": "items[-3:-1] 不含最后一个元素。要最后 3 个应写 items[-3:]。"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_type",
      "difficulty": "easy",
      "act": 2,
      "title": "字符串拼接当加法",
      "lang": "js",
      "lines": [
        "const a = prompt('数字');",
        "const b = prompt('数字');",
        "const sum = a + b;",
        "// 输入 2 和 3,结果是 '23'"
      ],
      "bugLine": 2,
      "hint": "prompt 返回的是什么类型?",
      "explain": "prompt 返回字符串,+ 变成拼接。要先 Number(a)+Number(b)。"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_null",
      "difficulty": "mid",
      "act": 2,
      "title": "空指针访问",
      "lang": "js",
      "lines": [
        "function getName(user) {",
        "    return user.profile.name;",
        "}",
        "",
        "getName({}); // 崩溃"
      ],
      "bugLine": 1,
      "hint": "user.profile 一定存在吗?",
      "explain": "user 没有 profile 时,访问 .name 抛错。应用可选链 user?.profile?.name。"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_mutate",
      "difficulty": "mid",
      "act": 2,
      "title": "遍历中删除",
      "lang": "python",
      "lines": [
        "def drop_zeros(nums):",
        "    for n in nums:",
        "        if n == 0:",
        "            nums.remove(n)",
        "    return nums"
      ],
      "bugLine": 3,
      "hint": "边遍历边改动同一个列表会怎样?",
      "explain": "遍历时 remove 会打乱索引,漏删元素。应遍历副本或用列表推导 [n for n in nums if n]。"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_await",
      "difficulty": "mid",
      "act": 3,
      "title": "漏了 await",
      "lang": "js",
      "lines": [
        "async function load() {",
        "    const res = fetch('/api/data');",
        "    const json = res.json();",
        "    return json;",
        "}"
      ],
      "bugLine": 1,
      "hint": "fetch 返回的是什么?Promise 还是结果?",
      "explain": "fetch 返回 Promise,漏 await 拿到的是 Promise 而非响应。应 const res = await fetch(...)。"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_closure",
      "difficulty": "mid",
      "act": 3,
      "title": "循环里的闭包",
      "lang": "js",
      "lines": [
        "for (var i = 0; i < 3; i++) {",
        "    setTimeout(() => console.log(i), 0);",
        "}",
        "// 打印 3 3 3,而不是 0 1 2"
      ],
      "bugLine": 0,
      "hint": "var 的作用域是?",
      "explain": "var 是函数作用域,所有回调共享同一个 i。把 var 改成 let(块级作用域)即可。"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_intdiv",
      "difficulty": "mid",
      "act": 3,
      "title": "整数除法",
      "lang": "python",
      "lines": [
        "def average(total, count):",
        "    return total // count",
        "",
        "# average(10, 4) 得到 2,期望 2.5"
      ],
      "bugLine": 1,
      "hint": "// 和 / 有什么不同?",
      "explain": "// 是整除,丢掉小数。求平均应用 / 得到浮点结果。"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_offbyone",
      "difficulty": "mid",
      "act": 3,
      "title": "边界差一",
      "lang": "js",
      "lines": [
        "function sum(arr) {",
        "    let s = 0;",
        "    for (let i = 0; i <= arr.length; i++) {",
        "        s += arr[i];",
        "    }",
        "    return s; // 结果是 NaN"
      ],
      "bugLine": 2,
      "hint": "i 最大能取到哪?",
      "explain": "i <= arr.length 会多访问一次越界的 undefined,导致 NaN。应为 i < arr.length。"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_race",
      "difficulty": "hard",
      "act": 4,
      "title": "并发数据错乱",
      "lang": "js",
      "lines": [
        "let balance = 100;",
        "async function withdraw(n) {",
        "    const b = balance;",
        "    await delay(10);",
        "    balance = b - n;",
        "}",
        "// 并发两笔,少扣了钱"
      ],
      "bugLine": 2,
      "hint": "读和写之间隔了一个 await,会发生什么?",
      "explain": "先读快照再异步写,两笔并发会用同一个旧快照,后写覆盖前写(竞态)。需加锁或原子操作。"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_leak",
      "difficulty": "hard",
      "act": 4,
      "title": "内存泄漏",
      "lang": "js",
      "lines": [
        "function mount(el) {",
        "    window.addEventListener('resize', onResize);",
        "}",
        "function unmount(el) {",
        "    // 忘了 removeEventListener",
        "}"
      ],
      "bugLine": 4,
      "hint": "加了监听,销毁时做了什么?",
      "explain": "卸载时没 removeEventListener,监听器和闭包一直被引用,内存泄漏。unmount 里要移除监听。"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_recur",
      "difficulty": "hard",
      "act": 4,
      "title": "无限递归",
      "lang": "python",
      "lines": [
        "def factorial(n):",
        "    return n * factorial(n - 1)",
        "",
        "# factorial(5) 栈溢出"
      ],
      "bugLine": 1,
      "hint": "递归什么时候停?",
      "explain": "没有终止条件,无限递归导致栈溢出。要加 if n <= 1: return 1 的基线。"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_float",
      "difficulty": "hard",
      "act": 5,
      "title": "浮点比较",
      "lang": "js",
      "lines": [
        "function isSum(a, b) {",
        "    return a + b === 0.3;",
        "}",
        "",
        "isSum(0.1, 0.2); // false!"
      ],
      "bugLine": 1,
      "hint": "0.1 + 0.2 在计算机里等于?",
      "explain": "浮点误差让 0.1+0.2 ≈ 0.30000000000000004,直接 === 会 false。应比较差值 < 一个极小 epsilon。"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_sqli",
      "difficulty": "hard",
      "act": 5,
      "title": "SQL 注入",
      "lang": "js",
      "lines": [
        "function findUser(name) {",
        "    const q = \"SELECT * FROM u WHERE name='\" + name + \"'\";",
        "    return db.query(q);",
        "}"
      ],
      "bugLine": 1,
      "hint": "name 如果是恶意字符串会怎样?",
      "explain": "字符串拼接 SQL 会被注入攻击(如 name=\"' OR '1'='1\")。必须用参数化查询/预编译语句。"
    },
    {
      "id": "p_shallow",
      "difficulty": "hard",
      "act": 5,
      "title": "浅拷贝陷阱",
      "lang": "js",
      "lines": [
        "const a = { list: [1, 2] };",
        "const b = { ...a };",
        "b.list.push(3);",
        "// a.list 也变成 [1,2,3] 了!"
      ],
      "bugLine": 1,
      "hint": "展开运算符拷贝的是引用还是值?",
      "explain": "{...a} 是浅拷贝,嵌套的 list 仍是同一个引用,改 b 影响 a。深层需深拷贝(如 structuredClone)。"
    }
  ],
